The paper discusses the problem of phase retrieval, which is a fundamental problem in signal processing and imaging. The problem is relevant to several areas of computer science, including information theory (cs.IT), computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), numerical analysis (cs.NA), and signal processing (cs.SI). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories that this paper belongs to, ordered from most to least likely.
